<p>Earlier this month, Charlotte teased her return to the series as she uploaded a behind-the-scenes shot alongside the caption: 'Feels good to be back'. </p>

<p>The brunette is currently dating videographer Liam Beaumont, after splitting from her boyfriend of two years Joshua Ritchie in November 2019. </p>

<p>During her time in the spotlight, the TV star has been involved in a series of high-profile romances, including flings with Scotty T, Max Morley and Stephen Bear. </p>

